---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  current="how"
  title="How RRS Realty Group Works, Get Matched With a Local Agent"
  description="See how RRS Realty Group personally connects Southeast Wisconsin homeowners and buyers with the right local agent, a real conversation and a hand-matched introduction, not a generic lead queue. Free, no obligation."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">A personal process</p>
      <h1>How RRS Connects You With the Right Agent</h1>
      <p>No anonymous lead queue, no random handoff. A real person reaches out, listens, and personally matches you to the right local agent. Here's exactly what happens.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:48px">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><h3>Tell Us About Your Move</h3><p>Fill out a short form with where your home is, your timeline, and what you're hoping to do. It's just enough for us to start a real conversation, no commitment.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><h3>We Reach Out and Listen</h3><p>A real person from RRS personally contacts you to talk it through, your goals, your home, your situation. You're never a file in a queue waiting for a stranger to call.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><h3>We Connect You With the Right Agent</h3><p>We partner with a team of trusted agents. With your situation in mind, we personally connect you with the right one for you, plus any other resources you need. A tailored fit, on your terms, with no obligation.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section area">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <p class="eyebrow">Common questions</p>
        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Is It Really Free?</h3><p>Yes. Our matching service costs homeowners and buyers nothing. There's no fee to get connected with an agent.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Am I Obligated to Anything?</h3><p>No. Getting matched doesn't commit you to listing, buying, or hiring anyone. You're always free to walk away.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>Who Are the Agents?</h3><p>Licensed Wisconsin real estate professionals who work in your specific area and have a track record we've reviewed.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>How Fast Will I Hear Back?</h3><p>Quickly, a real person from RRS reaches out personally to start the conversation, so you're not left waiting in a queue for a stranger to pick up.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>What Areas Do You Cover?</h3><p>All eight counties of Southeast Wisconsin, from Milwaukee and Waukesha to Racine, Kenosha, and the surrounding communities.</p></div>
        <div class="why-card"><h3>What If It's Not a Good Fit?</h3><p>Just let us know. The goal is the right match for you, not a forced one, there's no pressure to continue.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Ready to Get Matched?</h2>
      <p>It takes under two minutes and there's no obligation. Tell us about your move and we'll handle the rest.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/get-started/">Find my agent →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
